snippet.title: Cyber Storm Edge - Trailer (after redesign update)
snippet.description:
Challenging 2D platforming in retro style! Fight against Cyber Space Pirates!

This new version of the game redesigns the main character for him to look better, has a completely remade OST and the character has an idle animation! No modifications to level design nor physics were made. 

I hope people enjoy this update/new version! It's available on itchio and will be coming to Steam!
